data.description:
PRICE IMPROVEMENT, bring all offers! This ideal 2/2 condo with elevator and stairway access to 3rd floor, is safely tucked away in a gated community, with lots of amenities including fitness center, clubhouse, pool, cabana area, carwash station, lush greenways with fountains, and walking trails with dog waste/cleanup receptacles. Once inside enjoy your spacious split floorplan arrangement and screened lanai, fully equipped kitchen w/white cabinetry, pantry closet, updated faucet, and GE suite appliances. Both bathrooms have been tastefully updated as well. Laundry closet with included W/D.  HVAC-2016. Water/Sewer, Pest control & Gate access are all included in monthly fees.
Bring your VA Buyers as well. Condo is being listed for RENT as well and listing will be removed if lease is signed Multiple shops and restaurants are nearby and within walking/biking distance.  Culvers' and their famous ice cream is just down the street and Ikea is right around the corner as well.  St John's Town Center is not far either. Great access to I-295 & beaches.
